actions.text: House Committee on Rules Reported an Original Measure. Report No: 99-553.
Considered by House Agreed to Suspend the Rules by Yea-Nay Vote: 333-68 (2/3's Required) Record Vote No: 97.
Resolution Agreed to in House by Voice Vote.

official_title: A resolution vacating the proceedings by which H. Res. 427 was adopted by the House on April 22, 1986, and providing that said resolution shall be considered to have been laid on the table.

summary.text: Vacates the proceedings by which H. Res. 427 (Members' outside earned income limitations) was adopted by the House of Representatives and provides that such resolution shall be considered to have been laid on the table.
